3 (g) (1) In the event a qualified volunteer who has completed 25 years of
4 certified service dies, a death OR BURIAL benefit up to [$10,000] $14,000 shall be payable.
5 (2) In the event a volunteer who is receiving benefits under Subsection (h)
6 of this section dies, a DEATH OR burial benefit up to [$336] $560 for each year of certified
7 service shall be payable.
8 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect July
9 1, 2026.
